uot;你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=fef8d47d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"3d8870d29ff6e8e60fafbe416228502d5dbbdee6","tid":1818203,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8eae60b46c54f4a373f41a2a8285e4d0cd8333","tid":1818203,"uid":344348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d886c2474fcb85802f51fd4672757e5f8c6584","tid":1818203,"uid":250234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffebf1fdeea424f524b67a9024a043302943cdf7","tid":1818203,"uid":344348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d1878f6703b839b1b70984778bba09735ab0bac","tid":1818203,"uid":250234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"陪傾！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:31:41.000Z","msg":"心情好差，挂住我阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:41:53.000Z","msg":"伯母做咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"有cancer，走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d14fac3461149ecf3b9a6e38dcebf64010f4ee6","tid":1818203,"uid":250234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8eae60b46c54f4a373f41a2a8285e4d0cd8333","tid":1818203,"uid":344348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d886c2474fcb85802f51fd4672757e5f8c6584","tid":1818203,"uid":250234,"like":0,"dislike":